Project Detail Validation Fix Log
=================================
Test Time: 2025-06-17 13:45
Purpose: Fix validation errors in project detail endpoints

Issue:
- When opening a project, got "failed to load chat session" error
- Backend logs showed: "Input should be a valid dictionary or instance of ProjectInfo [type=model_type, input_value=ProjectResponse..."

Root Cause:
- ChatSessionResponse expects ProjectInfo object for the project field
- Code was passing ProjectResponse object instead
- Same issue in DocumentResponse

Fix Applied:
1. In get_project_sessions_endpoint:
   - Import ProjectInfo from chat_history_routes
   - Changed from ProjectResponse to ProjectInfo when creating the project object

2. In get_project_documents_endpoint:
   - Changed DocumentResponse model to expect ProjectInfo instead of ProjectResponse
   - Changed from ProjectResponse to ProjectInfo when creating the project object

3. Added import at top of file:
   - from src.server.chat_history_routes import ProjectInfo

Current Status:
- Backend restarted successfully
- Validation errors should be resolved
- Project detail view should now load sessions and documents properly

Next: User should test opening a project again to verify the fix works.